Rules:
- Include at least 3 SMART goals.
- Include at least 3 distinct user personas.
- Every user persona must have at least one user story.
- Requirements must use MoSCoW labelling (at least 2 Must Haves, 1 Should Have, 1 Could Have, 1 Won't Have).
- Include at least 3 success metrics, each with a measurable target.
- Include at least 2 milestones.
- Non-goals must be explicit and scope-bounding, not vague.
- Risks must include both a probability assessment and a mitigation strategy.
- Do not include markdown fences or prose outside the JSON.
